                <p><strong>Rosemary oil treatment:</strong> Mix 3-4 drops of rosemary essential oil with 1 tablespoon of coconut oil. Apply to the scalp and massage thoroughly. Use three times a week — overnight application works best. Research has proven that rosemary oil stimulates hair regrowth.</p>

                <p><strong>Maintain scalp health:</strong> If you have <a href="../dandruff-treatment-in-gurgaon">dandruff or other scalp issues</a>, treat those first. A clean scalp leads to better recovery.</p>

                <h2>Clinical Treatments — Fast-Track Your Recovery</h2>
                <p>If you do not see significant improvement after 3-4 months of home care, or if the hair fall is particularly severe, clinical treatments can be extremely beneficial.</p>

                <h3>PRP Therapy — The Best Treatment for Post-Covid Hair Loss</h3>
                <p><a href="../hair-prp-treatment-in-gurgaon">PRP (Platelet-Rich Plasma) therapy</a> is especially effective for post-covid hair fall. This is because it delivers growth factors directly to the dormant follicles. For follicles that have entered the resting phase after Covid, PRP serves as a powerful reactivation stimulus.</p>

                <p>Typically, 3 sessions are recommended at monthly intervals. Improvement usually becomes visible after the second session. The procedure is safe as it uses your own blood. There is no downtime, and you can resume your normal routine the same day. Our <a href="prp-hair-treatment-natural-way-to-regrow-hair.php">PRP treatment guide</a> explains the entire process in detail.</p>

                <h3>LED Light Therapy</h3>
